CatDescriptText: Cutline of images published in the Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 13, 1954, pg. 12 reads: " More Queen Contestants - Another group of Pittsburgh teen-agers who are clamoring to wear the crown of Hill City Queen includes, left to right,...Lois Squires...Barbara Hinton...Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Two frames: Portrait of Lois Squires wearing dark short sleeve knit top, posed in front of light colored background in Harris Studio for Hill City Teen Queen contest; Portrait of Barbara Hinton wearing light colored short sleeve lace sweater, posed in front of light colored background in Harris Studio for Hill City Teen Queen contest
